# ==============================================================================
# FILE        : high-ports.conf.example
# ==============================================================================
# Synopsis    : Example batch listener configuration — high/ephemeral ports
# Description : One port per line. Lines starting with # are comments; blank
#               lines are ignored; invalid lines are skipped with a warning.
#               Inline comments are NOT supported: a port must be alone on its
#               line. Use with:
#               socat-manager batch --file high-ports.conf.example
# Notes       : All ports here are above 1024 and bind without root.
# Version     : 1.0.2
# ==============================================================================

10000
10001
10002
20000
30000
40000
# Start of the dynamic/ephemeral range
49152
55555
